* Hyperbolic sine: the odd part of the exponential function, that is, formula_1
* Hyperbolic cosine: the even part of the exponential function, that is, formula_2
* Hyperbolic tangent: formula_3
* Hyperbolic cotangent: for , formula_4
* Hyperbolic secant: formula_5
